{"tid":2154684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"易志明相信恢復經香港轉機安排助內地生到海外求學","createTime":"2020-08-13T09:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T10:14:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5aec49bf2132c536d6ab96f04883ad69fd8058cd","tid":2154684,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:15:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543521-20200813.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543521-20200813.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=4ecc7fc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543521-20200813.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d40bcd62\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543521-20200813.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n航運交通界立法會議員易志明相信，機管局星期六起可讓內地出發旅客經香港轉機的安排，主要幫助內地學生到海外求學。<br />\n<br />\n易志明在本台節目說，內地除了個別地方仍有較多新增新型肺炎確診個案外，整體疫情是可以的，比香港還安全，形容有關安排是可以接受。他又認為，本港機場可恢復部份活動，對機場收入有幫助。"},{"pid":"17e43024fa5fdd80d6ec9b883cd053eb79fef536","tid":2154684,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:15:50.000Z","msg":"中國海外留學生關我鬼事？"},{"pid":"a7cfd9fb6edfa429447f51f104fbb516fc2e0ecc","tid":2154684,"uid":55010,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"點解幫佢地整死我地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04acfac17a079daed4fdc545cd72c984c8036c2d","tid":2154684,"uid":160102,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:42:38.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母，呢d咪係仆街囉"},{"pid":"df750b76630f7b7721018b3c3b08500a3c0e45af","tid":2154684,"uid":1544,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:52:27.000Z","ms